## Recommendations

Right now Acorns offers a very simple investing structure.  They have their customers answer simple profile questions and based on the customer's response they recommend a certain Acorns ETF based on the customer's risk profile.  The customer is able to choose different ETFs, however, the investement options are pre-defined by their portfolio managers. 

